---
title: Orange-Infused Dark Chocolate Mousse Pots with Almond Butter Crumb | Serves 4+
description: Rich, decadent and super simple to make, these orange dark chocolate mousse pots are seriously indulgent. Leave them with
enough time to set in the fridge, then top them with a super crunchy almond butter crumb and watch how quickly they'll
become your favourite sweet treat.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/603c7349046fce264a090a5e-e760db76.jpg
